## âš™ï¸ Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/log-analyzer.git
   cd log-analyzer
   ```
2. Create a virtual environment:
   ```bash
   python -m venv .venv
   .venv\Scripts\activate   # Windows
   ```
3. Add a sample log file (`access.log`) with entries like:
   ```
   203.0.113.10 - - [27/Dec/2025:17:31:00] "POST /login" 401
   198.51.100.7  - - [27/Dec/2025:17:32:44] "GET /admin" 404
   ```
4. Run the analyzer:
   ```bash
   python log_analyzer.py
   ```

